memberdef.name: associer

briefdescription.para: Associe l'operateur au domaine_dis, le domaine_Cl_dis, et a l'inconnue de son equation.
Represents the diffusion operator with VDF discretization for scalar fields in axisymmetric coordinates.

detaileddescription.para: The diffusivity field is non-uniform. The associated iterator is of type Iterateur_VDF_Elem, and the associated evaluator is of type Eval_Diff_VDF_Elem_Axi.
